WEBVTT

02:21:39.483 --> 02:21:40.816
What is it, Georgekutty Chetta?

02:21:40.858 --> 02:21:41.899
-Jose!
-Yes.

02:21:41.941 --> 02:21:44.441
Go wait near my house
immediately.

02:21:45.274 --> 02:21:46.608
If Sahadevan turns up there,

02:21:47.024 --> 02:21:48.316
you must follow him closely.
